OL,6,FA Metropolitan Police officer has been
OL,7,Ffound guilty of assault after he
OL,8,Fwrongfully arrested a woman for bus
OL,9,Ffare evasion in front of her young son.
OL,11,FPC Perry Lathwood, 50, "manhandled"
OL,12,FJocelyn Agyemang during the arrest in
OL,13,FCroydon in July last year, causing
OL,14,Fbruises.
OL,16,FMs Agyemang and her son got off the
OL,17,Fbus at around 11am on July 21, 2023
OL,18,Fand she was asked to show she had paid
OL,19,Fher fare by a bus inspector.
