OL,6,FDeputy Senior District Judge Tan Ikran
OL,7,Fsaid it was "not necessary" for
OL,8,FLathwood to "grab the woman's arm,
OL,9,Farrest her and handcuff her".
OL,11,FHe added: "There were not reasonable
OL,12,Fgrounds to suggest arrest was
OL,13,Fnecessary.
OL,15,F"The officer made an error of judgment
OL,16,Fand over reacted."
