OL,6,FPaul Jarvis, prosecuting told the
OL,7,Ftrial Lathwood put a hand on Ms
OL,8,FAgyemang, but she moved away, so he
OL,9,Fthen grabbed her arm and arrested her
OL,10,Ffor fare evasion.
OL,12,FThe incident was filmed by a crowd
OL,13,Fthat had gathered, with those filming
OL,14,Fasking Lathwood why he had arrested
OL,15,Fher.
OL,17,FMr Jarvis said Lathwood continued to
OL,18,Fhold her, demanding she tap her card.
OL,19,FHe also handcuffed her.
