OL,6,FAnother officer took her Oyster card
OL,7,Ffrom her hand and went away with it to
OL,8,Fsee if she had paid. It was confirmed
OL,9,Fthat Ms Agyemang had paid her fare and
OL,10,Fshe was de-arrested at the scene.
OL,12,FMs Agyemang said she felt "very
OL,13,Fviolated" by the incident.
OL,15,F"I just felt like they did not care,"
OL,16,Fshe said. "I just felt a bit degraded
OL,17,Fbecause I had not done anything wrong."
