OL,6,FScotland Yard said it did not intend
OL,7,Fto consider an accelerated misconduct
OL,8,Fhearing for the officer.
OL,10,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,11,F(IOPC) regional director Mel Palmer
OL,12,Fsaid: "Any use of force by officers
OL,13,Fshould be reasonable, proportionate
OL,14,Fand justifiable in the circumstances.
OL,16,F"This was a high-profile incident that
OL,17,Fcaused significant concern,
OL,18,Fparticularly in the Croydon community,
OL,19,Fafter footage of the incident was
OL,20,Fpublished online.
